  <description>
    <p>RVGL Launcher is a cross-platform installer, launcher and package manager for RVGL. This is a planned successor to the linux-only RVGL Installer script.</p>
    <p>Features</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Install and update game and content packs.</li>
        <li>View list of online events and join them directly.</li>
        <li>Enable or disable content packs on the fly.</li>
        <li>Add your own content repositories.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
